{"title": "Bus Stop",
  "author": "Donald Justice",
  "text": ["Lights are burning",
    "In quiet rooms",
    "Where lives go on",
    "Resembling ours.",
    "  ",
    "The quiet lives",
    "That follow us",
    "These lives we lead",
    "But do not own",
    "  ",
    "Stand in the rain",
    "So quietly",
    "When we are gone, ",
    "So quietly",
    "  ",
    "And the last bus",
    "Comes letting dark",
    "Umbrellas out",
    "Black flowers, black flowers.",
    "  ",
    "And lives go on.",
    "And lives go on.",
    "Like sudden lights",
    "At street corners",
    " ",
    "Or like the lights",
    "In quiet rooms",
    "Left on for hours, ",
    "Burning, burning."]
}
